<ab facs="#facs_494_r1l4"><expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> etc <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Johannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Ernſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvılhelm<ex>m</ex></expan> . vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_494_r1l5"><expan>pfallncʒgr<ex>afen</ex></expan> bey Reyn Vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> in Peyern etc Vnd dem <expan>wolgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_494_r1l6"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan> <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>Ötıng<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan> den dıe ſıe mıt Jn <expan>bringe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_494_r1l7"><expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . her gen <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> ʒu dem tag / den Jr gnade mıt dem <expan>Hochgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_494_r1l8"><expan>fürſt<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lud<ex>wig</ex></expan> <expan>pfallncʒgr<ex>afen</ex></expan> bey Reyn <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> in Peyern </ab>
