<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> etc., bekennen
                                                etc., daz wir den
                                                  <expan>hochgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>furst<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>marggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                                  <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> und
                                                  <expan>burggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                                  <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> etc.,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Johanns<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Ernst<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wilhelm<ex>m</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>pfallnczgr<ex>afen</ex></expan> bey Reyn
                                                und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> in
                                                Peyern etc., und dem
                                                  <expan>wolgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                                  <expan>Öting<ex>en</ex></expan>, und
                                                  <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan> den, die sie mit in
                                                  <expan>bringe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> her gen
                                                  <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> zu dem tag, den
                                                ir gnade mit dem
                                                  <expan>hochgeborn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>fürst<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Lud<ex>wig</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>pfallnczgr<ex>afen</ex></expan> bey Reyn,
                                                  <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog<ex>en</ex></expan> in
                                                Peyern und <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Mortani
                                                etc., zu <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> yecz
                                                suchen <expan>sülle<ex>n</ex></expan> und auch
                                                  <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan> den, die
                                                  <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> bey in hie seyn,
                                                auf <expan>demselbe<ex>n</ex></expan> tag und
                                                alslank derselb tag und teyding wern und vier tag
                                                darnach bey uns zu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
                                                geben <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>gebe<ex>n</ex></expan> ein frey, stark und
                                                sicher geleyt on alls geverde.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ip<ex>s</ex>a</expan> die
                                                  <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
                                                Lorencii.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab><expan>It<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ludweig von Peyern,
                                                  <expan>graf<ex>en</ex></expan> zu Mortani
                                                  <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan> ein
                                                revers <expan>mutat<ex>is</ex></expan>
<expan>muta<ex>n</ex>dis</expan> .</ab>
</div>
